{"tid":1773581,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【小店專訪：grannie kiddie店主】與香港人互撐 表態是每個人的基本權利","createTime":"2019-12-07T14:40:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T14:40:29.000Z","uid":301438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"05b55767936fe178ad82b7f69f8cd2e68914d93d","tid":1773581,"uid":301438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T14:40:29.000Z","msg":"【小店專訪：grannie kiddie店主】與香港人互撐 表態是每個人的基本權利<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/x-cIqMyf3A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fx-cIqMyf3A4&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=054f1ac4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/x-cIqMyf3A4</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><em>// 公開表態後，屋企人都會擔心，但我只是參與罷工，如果我不響應，反而會覺得不安樂；我們就是有權利去表態。如果我們都害怕，就真正被白色恐怖籠罩，變相就承認了它(的存在)。」//<br />\n<br />\n// 越多人發聲，加入黃店圈子，群眾力量就更大、更安全。//</em><br />\n</span><br />\ngrannie kiddie 是一間古著店，專門售賣古著及環保產品。店主Kaki熱愛穿古著，旅行時發現外國其實有很多古著的洋裝款式，希望引入更多古著，藉此推廣古著及環保文化，抗衡速食時裝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#黃色經濟圈 #黃店 #黃幫襯 #經濟線 #五大訴求缺一不可 #光復香港時代革命 #128維園見<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n港介線 FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kongazine/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkongazine%2F&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=a62a437a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kongazine/</a><br />\n港介線 IG: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/kongazine/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fkongazine%2F&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=a1924227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/kongazine/</a><br />\n<br />\ngrannie kiddie<br />\n香港古著店 Vintage Shop 👵🏻👧🏻<br />\nFB / IG: @granniekiddie<br />\n網店: <a href=\"http://granniekiddie.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgranniekiddie.com&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=a146e112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">granniekiddie.com</a><br />\n（實體店暫時停業｜網店繼續運作）"}]}